Yang Huang, Shih-Han Wang, Mohith Kamanuru, Luke E. K. Achenie, John R. Kitchin, and Hongliang Xin, Unifying theory of electronic descriptors of metal surfaces upon perturbation, Phys. Rev. B 110, L121404 (2024). &lt;a href="https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevB.110.L121404"&gt;https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevB.110.L121404&lt;/a&gt;.
